":"2020-11-18T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"趙麗穎個樣做乜咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0d590d0292b304ff4b9541134e3c6106b48d8b","tid":2290571,"uid":101756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:55:31.000Z","msg":"好撚賤<br />\n成日用人地國家法律漏洞<br />\n自己就永遠唔守法"},{"pid":"472f0ddf06106dfebfb671e3b622da1a8432fd03","tid":2290571,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:59:29.000Z","msg":"一陣美帝再BAN公司咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要佢係足夠理據懷疑都夠做啦<br />\n當人ON9?<br />\n仲要D人馬都係屎為過去"},{"pid":"624f0b398258312cd98c1101538ed57c7a72e4b4","tid":2290571,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:16:43.000Z","msg":"華為玩完！？ 出售旗下榮耀手機業務 芯片受制市場份額被侵蝕！ 〈蕭若元<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2290649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2290649</a>"}]}